        "title": "Refund Policy",
        "content": "<p>At <strong>Avemos®</strong>, customer satisfaction is our top priority. We stand behind our orthopedic travel pillow, which is why we offer an industry-leading <strong>30-Day Risk-Free Money-Back Guarantee</strong>.</p><h2>1. 30-Day Money-Back Guarantee</h2><p>We want you to be absolutely thrilled with your purchase. If you try the Avemos Travel Pillow and decide it doesn't suit your travel needs, you can return it within <strong>30 days</strong> of receiving the package for a 100% refund of the purchase price.</p><h2>2. Return Eligibility & Conditions</h2><p>To qualify for a refund under our guarantee:</p><ul><li>The product must be returned with all original packaging, tags, and travel accessories (e.g., the waterproof travel carry bag).</li><li>The pillow must not show excessive signs of wear, permanent stains, tear, or structural damage.</li><li>You must provide your order number or proof of purchase.</li></ul><h2>3. How to Initiate a Return</h2><p>Returning your pillow is simple:</p><ol><li>Send an email to our support team at <a href=\"mailto:support@avemosstore.com\">support@avemos.shop</a> with the subject line \"Return Request - [Your Order Number]\".</li><li>Briefly describe the reason for your return (we appreciate feedback to improve our product ergonomics!).</li><li>Our team will reply within 12-24 hours with return instructions and the warehouse mailing address.</li><li>Pack the pillow securely, ship it to the provided address, and email us the tracking code.</li></ol><h2>4. Return Shipping Cost</h2><p>Customers are responsible for paying the shipping costs for returning their items, unless the item arrived defective or damaged (see Section 6). Return shipping fees are non-refundable.</p><h2>5. Refund Processing</h2><p>Once your return is received and inspected at our logistics hub, we will send you an email to notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.</p><p>If approved, your refund will be processed immediately. A credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment within <strong>5 to 7 business days</strong>.</p><h2>6. Damaged or Defective Items</h2><p>We inspect every Avemos pillow before it leaves our warehouse. In the rare event that your product arrives damaged or defective, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:support@avemosstore.com\">support@avemos.shop</a> within 7 days of delivery with photos of the issue. We will send you a brand-new replacement pillow immediately at zero additional cost.</p>"
